Production network. Components used in production will be placed in this network. This means that production servers,
routers connected to WAN (that will be used development and production) etc will be located in the network.
172.31.64.0/18:
Production2. An Explanation was abbribiated.
172.31.128.0/18:
Development network. Components in development will be placed in this network. This means that development servers,
routers connected to "My Home Network" etc.
172.31.128.0/18:
Development or staging network.
